## Erling VM arguments.
## Runs as a single self-contained node in a container -- no distribution,
## no epmd, no remote shell exposed on the network.

-sname erling
-setcookie erling_local_only

## Do not start distribution at all: the bot is an outbound-only client and
## nothing needs to connect to its VM.
-start_epmd false
-proto_dist inet_tcp

+K true
+A 8

## Fail fast and let the container runtime restart us rather than limping on.
-heart false
